            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="30653584">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">看了一点点，没坚持看下去</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-02-24 17:04</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                看了一点点，没坚持看下去
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

